'''法國航空447號班機'''原定由[[巴西|巴西]][[里約熱內盧|里約熱內盧]][[里约热内卢/加利昂－安东尼奥·卡洛斯·若比姆国际机场|加利昂國際機場]]飛往[[法國|法國]][[巴黎|巴黎]][[戴高樂機場|戴高樂機場]]。2009年6月1日，該航班一架[[空中巴士A330|空中巴士A330-203]]客機（註冊編號：F-GZCP），載有216名乘客以及12名機組人員<ref>{{Cite web|title=法国一架载有228人的空客330-200客机失踪-搜狐新闻|url=http://news.sohu.com/20090601/n264272218.shtml|access-date=2021-08-21|work=news.sohu.com|archive-date=2019-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190203013849/http://news.sohu.com/20090601/n264272218.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，在[[巴西|巴西]][[圣佩德罗和圣保罗群岩|圣佩德罗和圣保罗岛]]屿附近坠毁<ref>{{Cite web|title=巴西空军证实法航失踪飞机残骸已经找到_新闻中心_新浪网|url=http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2009-06-02/205317936923.shtml|access-date=2021-08-21|work=news.sina.com.cn|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609152341/http://news.sina.com.cn/w/2009-06-02/205317936923.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，機上人員全數罹難。此空難為[[法國航空|法國航空]]成立以來最嚴重的[[空難|空難]]<ref name="Plane Crash Info">{{cite news|title=Plane Crash Info|url=http://planecrashinfo.com/2009/2009-24.htm|accessdate=2011-10-23|archive-date=2020-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200708005027/http://www.planecrashinfo.com/2009/2009-24.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/world/06/02/09/search-intensifies-vanished-air-france-flight|title=Search intensifies for vanished Air France flight|date=2009-06-02|agency=[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]|publisher=ABS–CBN Corporation|accessdate=2011-06-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110614141909/http://www.abs-cbnnews.com/world/06/02/09/search-intensifies-vanished-air-france-flight|archivedate=2011-06-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>，亦是A330最嚴重及首次商業飛行空難<ref>{{Cite web|title=ASN Aviation Safety Database|url=http://aviation-safety.net/database/dblist.php?field=typecode&var=023%&cat=%1&sorteer=datekey&page=1|accessdate=2013-12-26|year=2013|publisher=Flight Safety Foundation|archive-date=2021-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210127192124/http://aviation-safety.net/database/dblist.php?field=typecode&var=023%25&cat=%251&sorteer=datekey&page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>，更是[[天合联盟|天合联盟]]自成立以来死亡人数最多的空难。

事發後五天，[[巴西海軍|巴西海軍]]找到飛機的大型殘骸及兩具屍體，但揭露空難原因的[[飛行紀錄儀|飛行紀錄儀]]直到2011年5月在大西洋海底才找到<ref name="07-02-2009 BEA Report">{{cite web|title=Interim report on the accident on 1 June 2009 to the Airbus A330-203 registered F-GZCP operated by Air France flight AF 447 Rio de Janeiro – Paris|url=http://www.bea.aero/docspa/2009/f-cp090601e1.en/pdf/f-cp090601e1.en.pdf|accessdate=2009-07-04|date=2009-07-02|format=PDF|publisher=Bureau d'Enquêtes et d'Analyses pour la sécurité de l'aviation civile (BEA)|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503065807/http://www.bea.aero/docspa/2009/f-cp090601e1.en/pdf/f-cp090601e1.en.pdf|archive-date=2011-05-03|dead-url=no|location=Paris}} ([http://www.bea.aero/docspa/2009/f-cp090601e1/pdf/f-cp090601e1.pdf Original French version] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bea.aero/docspa/2009/f-cp090601e1/pdf/f-cp090601e1.pdf|date=20110531151859}}).</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Flight AF 447 on 1st June 2009|url=http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.af.447/flight.af.447.php|accessdate=2011-06-02|year=2011|publisher=BEA|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503065449/http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.af.447/flight.af.447.php|archive-date=2011-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。空難最後調查報告於2012年7月5日的新聞發佈會上公佈<ref name="Final">{{cite web|title=Final report on the accident on 1st June 2009 to the Airbus A330-203 registered F-GZCP operated by Air France flight AF 447 Rio de Janeiro – Paris|url=http://www.bea.aero/docspa/2009/f-cp090601.en/pdf/f-cp090601.en.pdf|date=July 2012|publisher=[[Bureau_d'Enquêtes_et_d'Analyses_pour_la_Sécurité_de_l'Aviation_Civile|BEA]]|page=217|access-date=2012-07-05|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112015601/https://www.bea.aero/docspa/2009/f-cp090601.en/pdf/f-cp090601.en.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Briefing|url=http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.af.447/point.presse.05juillet2012.en.php|accessdate=2013-02-24|date=2012-07-05|publisher=BEA|archive-date=2013-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131112111135/http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.af.447/point.presse.05juillet2012.en.php|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，指出[[皮托管|皮托管]]（pitot tube）結冰使飛機未能偵測空速，[[自動駕駛|自動駕駛]]自動關閉，機員錯誤操作導致失速，最後釀成空難<!--Section 4.1, page 79--><ref name="Final" /><ref name="NYToninterim3">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/30/world/europe/air-france-flight-447-crash-report-july-2011.html|first=Nicola|last=Clark|title=Report on Air France Crash Points to Pilot Training Issues|date=2011-07-29|work=The New York Times|accessdate=2014-03-22|archive-date=2021-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309021906/https://www.nytimes.com/2011/07/30/world/europe/air-france-flight-447-crash-report-july-2011.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

