== 事發經過 ==
2009年5月31日，班機在里約熱內盧當地時間19時29分起飛，原定於6月1日上午10時03分到達巴黎<ref name="Summary">{{cite web |title=Safety Investigation Following the Accident on 1st June 2009 to the Airbus A300-203, Flight AF 447 – Summary |url=http://www.bea.aero/fr/enquetes/vol.af.447/note05juillet2012.en.pdf |publisher=[[Bureau_d'Enquêtes_et_d'Analyses_pour_la_Sécurité_de_l'Aviation_Civile|BEA]] |format=PDF |date=July 2012 |accessdate=2014-03-22 |archive-date=2013-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123003826/http://www.bea.aero/fr/enquetes/vol.af.447/note05juillet2012.en.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[UTC|UTC]]01時35分，客機與航管作出最後一次通話，並在UTC1時49分離開巴西雷達監管範圍。當時機長迪布瓦及副機師博南在駕駛席上，而羅貝爾則在駕駛艙後方<ref>BEA first interim report, section 1.17.2.2</ref>。

UTC1時55分，機長離開座位去休息並換上副機師羅貝爾。當時博南為控制機師，而羅貝爾則為監控機師。UTC2時06分，機師通知空服員飛機將會進入[[亂流|亂流]]區域。之後飛機的皮托管因結冰而失效，無法偵測飛機速度，在系統發現了不正常數值的情況下，飞行控制模式切換至替代规律（Alternate law）。2時10分5秒，飛機解除了自動駕駛模式，之後自動節流閥亦自動解除，這意味機師們開始手動飛行。飛機由於受到亂流的影響而向右傾側，於是博南便把操縱桿左壓進行修正，但與此同時他卻抬高機鼻使飛機爬升，這動作在當時並沒有需要<ref>BEA final report, section 2.1.2.3 "The excessive amplitude of these [nose-up] inputs made them unsuitable and incompatible with the recommended aeroplane handling practices for high altitude flight."</ref>。據飛行紀錄儀的資料，當時飛機以每分鐘7000英尺(2130米)的高速率爬升，空速由274節(507km/h)瞬間降至52節(96km/h)<ref name="Palmer, p. 86">Palmer, p. 86</ref>。

皮托管結冰只維持了一分鐘多些<ref>Palmer, p. 7 "02:11:07 [...] The last of the pitot icing had cleared and all three airspeed indications were then displaying correctly"</ref><ref>Palmer, p. 57 "The pitot icing lasted for about one minute and five seconds".</ref><ref>BEA final report, p. 198 "The speed displayed on the left PFD was incorrect for 29 seconds, that of the speed on the ISIS for 54 seconds and the speed displayed on the right PFD for 61 seconds at most."</ref>，之後便回復正常。但飛機仍繼續增加攻角，2時11分10秒，飛機已爬升至3 8000英尺(1 1580米)，攻角達16度，推力全滿，2時11分15秒，飛機因為沒有升力開始下降，攻角又增加至30度。由於飞行控制规律在備用模式，系統原定自動推頭（將機首降低）的失速保護沒有啟動<ref>Palmer, pp. 78-80</ref> ，飛機陷入[[失速|失速]]卻沒有回復動作，這在刻意操作下也幾乎不可能出現在空中客车的飛機上。

2時11分40秒，機長返回駕駛艙。當時飛機攻角已達40度，飛機已降至3 5000英尺(1 0670米)，雖然指示器已經不結冰，失速警告卻未響起，這次是由於此時攻角過高，空速指示器值被判定無效<ref>Palmer, p. 57. "This created a situation where the air was pushing into, in addition to flowing over, the static ports. [...] This dynamic accounts for the repeated falling of the airspeed to invalid values."</ref>。22秒後，博南稍微降低機鼻，空速指示器恢復，失速警告間歇性響起。飛機下降至1 0000英尺(3050米)，此時機長發出重要訊息，博南應降低機鼻挽救失速。羅貝爾接管飛機操控權，飛機已下降至4000尺(1220米)。2000尺(610米)，[[地面迫近警告系統|地面迫近警告系統]]響起。飛行紀錄儀於2時14分28.4秒停止，最後一句說話為機長：「仰角10度（ten degrees pitch attitude.）」，撞擊時地速為107節(198km/h)，所有人員瞬間死亡<ref name="spiegel_2011_05_23">{{cite news|url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/europe/0,1518,764227,00.html|title=Recording Indicates Pilot Wasn't In Cockpit During Critical Phase|date=2011-05-23|accessdate=2014-03-22|archive-date=2011-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110525215411/http://www.spiegel.de/international/europe/0,1518,764227,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由3 8000英尺(1 1580米)至撞毀期間歷時3分30秒，整個過程飛機都處於失速狀態<ref name="bea2011may27">{{cite web|title=Flight AF 447 on 1st June 2009, A330-203, registered F-GZCP, 27 May 2011 briefing|url=http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.af.447/info27may2011.en.php|publisher=[[Bureau_d'Enquêtes_et_d'Analyses_pour_la_Sécurité_de_l'Aviation_Civile|BEA]]|accessdate=2014-03-22|archive-date=2015-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208144900/http://www.bea.aero/en/enquetes/flight.af.447/info27may2011.en.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>，記錄顯示駕駛直至墜機都不知道飛機已經失速。

== 搜救行动 ==
由於飛機離開雷達監控區，因此航管人員並不知道班機已失事。班機原定在在約UTC2時20分聯繫[[塞內加爾|塞內加爾]]空中管制區，並在3時45分進入[[維德角|維德角]]空中管制區。班機沒有聯繫塞內加爾航管，而航管亦曾嘗試聯繫法航447，但沒有回應。塞內加爾航管要求另一架法航459班機嘗試聯繫447號班機，亦沒有回應<ref>{{Citation | publisher = BEA | title = First interim report | chapter = Section 1.9.2 "Coordination between the control centres"}}.</ref>。

[[巴西空軍|巴西空軍]]隨即在[[费尔南多·迪诺罗尼亚群島|费尔南多·迪诺罗尼亚群島]]附近展開搜索，而法國偵察機亦在塞內加爾[[達喀爾|達喀爾]]起飛前往大西洋搜索<ref name="BBC1">{{Cite news |title=French plane lost in ocean storm |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/8076848.stm |publisher=BBC |accessdate=2009-06-01 |date=2009-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090603061124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/8076848.stm |archivedate=2009-06-03 |deadurl=no |quote=At 0530 GMT, Brazil's air force launched a search-and-rescue mission, sending out a coast guard patrol aircraft and a specialised air force rescue aircraft. … France is despatching three search planes based in Dakar }}</ref>。西班牙的C-235海上巡逻機<ref>[http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2009/06/01/espana/1243878943.html 西班牙方面新聞] {{Wayback|url=http://www.elmundo.es/elmundo/2009/06/01/espana/1243878943.html |date=20090605065258 }} {{sp}} 於2009年6月2日查閱</ref>和美國的[[P-3獵戶座海上巡邏機|P-3獵戶座海上巡邏機]]亦加入搜索行動<ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/fait-divers/premieres-precisions-sur-l-airbus-d-air-france-disparu_764282.html | title = Premières précisions sur l'Airbus d'Air France disparu | trans_title = First information about the disappeared Air France Airbus | date = 2009-06-01 | work = L'Express | language = fr | accessdate = 2009-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090605052346/http://www.lexpress.fr/actualite/societe/fait-divers/premieres-precisions-sur-l-airbus-d-air-france-disparu_764282.html | archivedate = 2009-06-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title= AF 447 may have come apart before crash: experts |url= http://ibnlive.in.com/news/af-447-may-have-come-apart-before-crash-experts/94037-2-p2.html |agency= [[Associated_Press|Associated Press]] |date= 2009-06-03 |accessdate= 2009-06-03 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090606062006/http://ibnlive.in.com/news/af-447-may-have-come-apart-before-crash-experts/94037-2-p2.html |archivedate= 2009-06-06 |deadurl= no }}</ref>。

6月1日上午，法航和法國政府已假設飛機失事且全數罹難，法航發言人向[[法國快報|法國快報]]說「沒有生還希望」<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.lexpansion.com/economie/actualite-economique/aucun-espoir-pour-le-vol-rio-paris-d-air-france_182359.html |script-title=fr:‘Aucun espoir’ pour le vol Rio-Paris d'Air France |trans_title=‘No hope’ for the Air France Rio – Paris flight |work=L'Express |language=fr |date=2009-06-01 |accessdate=2009-06-01 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090605172000/http://www.lexpansion.com/economie/actualite-economique/aucun-espoir-pour-le-vol-rio-paris-d-air-france_182359.html |archivedate=2009-06-05 |deadurl=no |title=存档副本 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | title= Air France 'loses hope' after plane drops off the radar en route from Brazil to Paris with 228 people on board | url= http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1190034/Air-France-plane-drops-radar-en-route-Brazil-Paris-228-people-board.html | work= Daily Mail | location= UK | date= 2009-06-01 | accessdate= 2009-06-01 | first= David | last= Williams | archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20090608050428/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/worldnews/article-1190034/Air-France-plane-drops-radar-en-route-Brazil-Paris-228-people-board.html | archivedate= 2009-06-08 | deadurl= no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news | url = http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jun/01/air-france-crash-a330-brazil | title = French plane crashed over Atlantic | date = 2009-06-01 | accessdate = 2009-06-01 | work = The Guardian | location = UK | first = Angelique | last = Chrisafis | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090611192232/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2009/jun/01/air-france-crash-a330-brazil | archivedate = 2009-06-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，[[法國|法國]]總統[[薩科齊|薩科齊]]向乘客親屬表示生還機會渺茫<ref name="WRAL">{{Cite news |title=Prospect slim of finding plane survivors |publisher=KKTV-TV |agency=Associated Press |url=http://www.kktv.com/home/headlines/46633847.html |date=2009-06-01 |accessdate=2011-02-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110713154614/http://www.kktv.com/home/headlines/46633847.html |archive-date=2011-07-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。6月2日UTC15時20分，巴西空軍發現費爾南多·迪諾羅尼亞島東北650公里，靠近[[圣佩德罗和圣保罗群岩|圣佩德罗和圣保罗群岩]]處發現殘骸及一帶長5公里的油漬，相信是航空煤油。該殘骸包括飛機座椅、桶、橘色浮標、白色物件和電子[[導體|導體]]<ref name="fab_3103">{{Cite news |title=Brazilian Air Force Bulletin |number=6 |url=http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3103 |date=2009-06-02 |language=pt |accessdate=2014-03-22 |archive-date=2009-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611165414/http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3103 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=NYT0602>{{Cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/03/world/europe/03plane.html |title=France and Brazil Press Search for Missing Plane |work=The New York Times |accessdate=2009-06-02 |date=2009-06-02 |first=Christine |last=Negroni |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606232052/http://www.nytimes.com/2009/06/03/world/europe/03plane.html |archivedate=2009-06-06 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。該天晚點與巴西乘客親屬會見後，[[巴西國防部|巴西國防部]]部長[[内尔松·若宾|内尔松·若宾]]宣佈所發現的殘骸相信是屬於法航447<ref name="CNNconfirm">{{Cite news|date=2009-06-02|url=http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/americas/06/02/brazil.france.plane.missing/index.html|title=No survivors found in wreckage of Air France jet, official says|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2009-06-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090606155453/http://www.cnn.com/2009/WORLD/americas/06/02/brazil.france.plane.missing/|archivedate=2009-06-06|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="BBCConfirm">{{Cite news|date=2009-06-02|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8080290.stm|title=Ocean search finds plane debris|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2009-06-02|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090603011653/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8080290.stm|archivedate=2009-06-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>。巴西代理總統[[若澤·阿倫卡爾|若澤·阿倫卡爾]]在當晚簽署法令，宣佈全國哀悼三天<ref name="BBCConfirm" /><ref>{{Cite news | date = 2009-06-02 | trans_title = José Alencar decrees three days official mourning for Airbus victims | url = http://g1.globo.com/Noticias/Brasil/0,,MUL1180489-5598,00-JOSE+ALENCAR+DECRETA+TRES+DIAS+DE+LUTO+OFICIAL+POR+VITIMAS+DO+AIRBUS.html | title = José Alencar decreta três dias de luto oficial por vítimas do Airbus | publisher = Globo | accessdate = 2009-06-02 | language = pt | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090612182822/http://g1.globo.com/Noticias/Brasil/0,,MUL1180489-5598,00-JOSE+ALENCAR+DECRETA+TRES+DIAS+DE+LUTO+OFICIAL+POR+VITIMAS+DO+AIRBUS.html | archivedate = 2009-06-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。同一天，法國海軍護衛艦风月號和[[西北風級兩棲突擊艦|西北風級兩棲突擊艦]]啟程前往懷疑事發地點。此外，法國[[研究船|研究船]]“為什麼不呢？號”（Pourquoi Pas?）聯同兩艘可潛入6,000米深的小型潛艇亦出發搜索<ref>{{Cite news |url= http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hCW-WX005nehnu4oOpI61nUXF0lA |title= Navy ships seek to recover Air France crash debris |first= Evaristo |last= Sá |date= 2009-06-03 |agency= Agence France-Presse |accessdate= 2014-03-22 |archive-date= 2009-06-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090608034907/http://www.google.com/hostednews/afp/article/ALeqM5hCW-WX005nehnu4oOpI61nUXF0lA |dead-url= no }}</ref> 。事發地點的深度可達4,700米<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.news24.com/Content/World/News/1073/27cddc2b46c04b558f783e845b6a4721/02-06-2009%2007-06/Mini-subs_sent_to_look_for_jet |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mr7zxXu7?url=http://www.news24.com/Content/World/News/1073/27cddc2b46c04b558f783e845b6a4721/02-06-2009%2007-06/Mini-subs_sent_to_look_for_jet |archivedate=2010-01-17 |date=2009-06-02 |accessdate=2009-06-02 |publisher=News24 |title=Mini-subs sent to look for jet |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Citation | publisher = BEA | title = First interim report | chapter = Section 1.16.1.1 "Context of the searches"}}.</ref>。6月3日，巴西海軍[[巡邏艇|巡邏艇]]格拉雅烏號（Grajaú）最先抵達發現殘骸的地點，而巴西海軍共派出五艘船前往。

6月3日，法航發言人表示事發當天收到班機[[飞机通信寻址与报告系统|飞机通信寻址与报告系统]]傳來超過三分鐘的電子訊息，訊息在UTC2時10分至14分期間傳送了共6項故障報告及19項警告<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://jt.france2.fr/20h/ |title=France 2 |language=fr |format=video |access-date=2009-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090706215400/http://jt.france2.fr/20h/ |archive-date=2009-07-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，其中包括[[皮托静压系统|皮托静压系统]]故障<ref name="JASC codes">{{cite web|url=http://av-info.faa.gov/sdrx/documents/JASC_Code.pdf|title=Joint aircraft system/component code table and definitions|publisher=Federal Aviation Administration, USA|accessdate=2009-06-06|archive-date=2009-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090510212148/http://av-info.faa.gov/sdrx/documents/JASC_Code.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>、[[大氣資料慣性基準系統|大氣資料慣性基準系統]]（Air Data Inertial Reference Unit）故障導致[[自動駕駛|自動駕駛]]系統以及[[自動節流閥|自動節流閥]]關閉、[[空中防撞系統|空中防撞系統]]切換至故障模式、飛行控制規律切換至備用模式。2時10分，飛機傳送了一段包括飛機[[經緯度|經緯度]]{{Coord|2.98|N|30.59|W|type:event|display=inline|format=dms}}的訊息。2時12分，發出警告表示飛機三組大气数据系统不一致。2時14分，發出最後一組數據，指客艙的垂直速度過高<ref name=AvHer090602>{{Cite news|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=41a81ef1/0004&opt=0|title=Crash: Air France A332 over Atlantic on 1 June 2009, aircraft lost|work=Aviation Herald|date=2009-06-02|accessdate=2020-09-12|archive-date=2019-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190316131201/http://avherald.com/h?article=41a81ef1%2F0004&opt=0|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.airbusdriver.net/airbus_fltlaws.htm |title=Airbus Flight Control Laws |publisher=Airbus |accessdate=2009-06-03 |archive-date=2009-04-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090416112524/http://www.airbusdriver.net/airbus_fltlaws.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://web.archive.org/web/20090606090922/http://www.airbus.com/index.php?id=276|title=Avionics Product Range |publisher=Airbus |accessdate=2011-08-21}}</ref>。

6月6日，即失事後的五天，發現兩具男性屍體及座椅<ref name=nota17>{{cite web|url=http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3136|title=Press Release 17: Information on Searches of the Air France Flight 447|date=2009-06-06|publisher=Brazilian Ministry of Defense|accessdate=2013-11-17|deadurl=no|archive-date=2009-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090611145544/http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3136}}</ref>，此外亦發現內有電腦和疫苗接種卡的尼龍背包，及內有法航登機證的皮革[[公事包|公事包]]<ref name="bodies found">{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/8087303.stm |title=Bodies 'found' from missing plane |date=2009-06-06 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2009-06-06 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090608084609/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/americas/8087303.stm |archivedate=2009-06-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/31137068/|title=Brazil: Bodies found near Air France crash site|date=2009-06-06|publisher=[[MSNBC|MSNBC]]|accessdate=2009-06-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090607085129/http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/31137068/|archivedate=2009-06-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>。6月7日，找到首個飛機重要大型殘骸－[[垂直尾翼|垂直尾翼]]<ref name=BBCtail>{{Cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8089917.stm|title=Air France tail section recovered|publisher=BBC News|date=2009-06-08|accessdate=2010-01-01|archive-date=2012-04-04|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/66gAfSkOn?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8089917.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在接下來的一星期，巴西軍方共動員了1,100人、<ref name=nota39>{{cite web|url=http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3262|title=Press Release 39: Information on Searches of the Air France Flight 447|date=2009-06-22|publisher=Brazilian Ministry of Defense|accessdate=2013-11-17|deadurl=no|archive-date=2009-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091125230600/http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3262}}</ref>15架航空器參與搜救<ref name=nota37>{{cite web|url=http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3252|title=Press Release 37: Information on Searches of the Air France Flight 447|date=2009-06-20|publisher=Brazilian Ministry of Defense|accessdate=2013-11-17|deadurl=no|archive-date=2009-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090624014556/http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3252}}</ref>。[[巴西航空工業R99|巴西航空工業R99]]飛機共飛行超過100小時，機上的電子儀器掃瞄了超過100萬平方公里海域<ref name=nota31>{{cite web|url=http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3180|title=Press Release 31: Information on Searches of the Air France Flight 447|date=2009-06-14|publisher=Brazilian Ministry of Defense|accessdate=2013-11-17|deadurl=no|archive-date=2009-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620122837/http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3180}}</ref>，其他飛機亦以目視方式搜索了超過32萬平方公里海域<ref name=nota39/>。

6月10日，法國的[[翡翠号核潜艇|翡翠号核潜艇]]抵達事發海域尋找可能已沉至海底的飛行記錄儀（俗稱黑盒）<ref name="cbc_nuclear">{{Cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2009/06/05/air-france-search-debris-black-box469.html |title=France sends nuclear sub to hunt for jet wreckage |publisher=CBC News |date=2009-06-05 |accessdate=2009-06-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090608161905/http://www.cbc.ca/world/story/2009/06/05/air-france-search-debris-black-box469.html |archivedate=2009-06-08 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。水面搜索結束後，水底搜索仍然進行。[[法国航空事故调查处|法国航空事故调查处]]主席表示他對找到黑盒的可能性並不樂觀，黑盒可能沉至3,000米下地形崎嶇的海底<ref name=BBC3>{{Cite news |title=Lost jet data 'may not be found' |publisher=BBC |date=2009-06-03 |accessdate=2009-06-03 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8080669.stm |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090604025646/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/8080669.stm |archivedate=2009-06-04 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

6月19日，兩群相隔80公里共50具屍體被尋回<ref>{{Cite news |first=Matthew |last=Campbell |author2=Richard Woods |title=Crash jet 'split in two at high altitude' |date=2009-06-14 |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/europe/article6493728.ece |work=The Times |location=UK |accessdate=2009-06-14 }}</ref><ref name="BRMOD_Nota33">{{cite web|url=http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3215|title=Note 33: Information on Searches of the Air France Flight 447|date=2009-06-16|publisher=Brazilian Ministry of Defense|accessdate=2009-06-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090620000139/http://www.fab.mil.br/portal/capa/index.php?mostra=3215|archivedate=2009-06-20|deadurl=no}}</ref>。病理學家根據牙齒和手指模檢驗了50具屍體，包括機長迪布瓦<ref>BEA second interim report, section 1.13, page 32 (PDF page 33 of 104) "The autopsies made it possible to identify fifty persons: 45 passengers, 4 flight attendants, and the captain"</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/news/world/us_and_americas/article6559861.ece|title=Hopes of finding Air France Airbus black boxes dashed|work=The Times |location=London |date=2009-06-23  | accessdate=2010-04-23 | first1=Charles | last1=Bremner | first2=Sophie | last2=Tedmanson}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.lefigaro.fr/flash-actu/2009/06/25/01011-20090625FILWWW00400-af-447-le-corps-du-pilote-identifie.php|work=Le Figaro|language=fr|location=France|title=INFO FIGARO – AF 447 : le corps du pilote identifié|date=2009-06-25|accessdate=2014-03-22|archive-date=2009-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090628052754/http://www.lefigaro.fr/flash-actu/2009/06/25/01011-20090625FILWWW00400-af-447-le-corps-du-pilote-identifie.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月26日宣佈終止搜索行動，在英、法、西、美的協助下共尋回50具屍體和640件碎片<ref>BEA first interim report, section 1.12.1, page 37 (PDF page 38 of 128)</ref>。惟至7月中，飛機黑盒仍未被找回，此時黑盒因電池消耗完畢而不再發出訊號，一度令飛機失事的原因石沉大海<ref name="France24230609">{{Cite news|title=Investigators say they have no confirmed black-box signals|url=http://www.france24.com/en/20090623-airbus-a330-air-france-crash-black-boxes-signal-located-monde-report|publisher=France 24.com|date=2009-06-27|accessdate=2009-06-23|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090626061559/http://www.france24.com/en/20090623-airbus-a330-air-france-crash-black-boxes-signal-located-monde-report|archivedate=2009-06-26|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

